Invocation Name: symptom checker
des:
Symptom Checker will ask several questions about common symptoms of the specified condition. Currently there are two conditions available, Sleep Apnea and Generalized Anxiety Disorder (GAD). More conditions will be added in the future. The questionnaires take about one to three minutes to complete.

This skill does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only. This skill is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice, and if you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
